Global Intelligent Household Gas Alarm Market Insights
Intelligent Household Gas Alarm Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.7% from 2024 to 2030.

Intelligent Household Gas Alarm Market Overview
The global intelligent household gas alarm market is projected to grow from USD 1.5 billion in 2023 to approximately USD 2.8 billion by 2032, reflecting a robust compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by increasing awareness of residential safety and government regulations mandating the installation of gas detection systems in residential buildings. Rising urbanization, coupled with technological advancements in smart home systems, further propels the demand for efficient and reliable gas alarm solutions.

